    "updated_at": "2025-12-16T21:21:17Z",
    "body": "I'm encountering this with `git` worktrees that are created using [`phantom`](https://github.com/aku11i/phantom).\n\nExample:\n```\n❯ pwd\n/Users/mscottford/code/example\n\nexample on  main\n❯ phantom create feature-branch\nCreated worktree 'feature-branch' at /Users/mscottford/code/example/.git/phantom/worktrees/feature-branch\n\nexample on  main\n❯ phantom shell feature-branch\nEntering worktree 'feature-branch' at /Users/mscottford/code/example/.git/phantom/worktrees/feature-branch\nType 'exit' to return to your original directory\n\n\nfeature-branch on  feature-branch\n❯ pwd\n/Users/mscottford/code/example/.git/phantom/worktrees/feature-branch\n\nfeature-branch on  feature-branch\n❯\n```",
